Albert Leroy was the son of a 38-year-old preacher named Albert Redfield  (born in 1841).  His grandfather, James, was born in 1802. When my great-great-grandfather was born Thomas Jefferson was president.

Old fathers seem to be the norm in this branch of the family.  Ages when their sons were born:  

    Albert Leroy 52
    Albert Redfield 38
    James 39. 

... 

